ile app.";i:37;s:110:"Without needing too much technical expertise these can be enabled and actively monitored all with the MyQ app.";i:38;s:138:"Once installed the Chamberlain MyQ Garage will give you the peace of mind of knowing your garage door is closed even when youre not there.";i:39;s:138:"You can control and monitor the door from anywhere and the app will make sure you receive alerts any time there is activity with the door.";i:40;s:201:"The wireless garage door opener is far older than the Internet but todays connected technologies have added new capabilities for monitoring and sharing access to your garage from anywhere in the world.";i:41;s:176:"With the help of mobile apps not only will your smartphone replace your garages remote control but youll also get reminders when youve left the door open easily manage who can.";}}